    <questiontext format="moodle_auto_format">
				<text><![CDATA[<p class="HELM_exercise">Exercise</p>
<p>Simplify \({@a1@}\times 10^{@ind1@}\times{@b1@}\times 10^{@ind2@}\).</p>

<p>[[input:ans1]] [[validation:ans1]]</p>]]></text>
		</questiontext>
    <generalfeedback format="moodle_auto_format">
				<text><![CDATA[<p>We multiply the two numbers \({@a1@}\) and \({@b1@}\) then using our first law of indices we add the powers of 10.&nbsp;</p><p>So we get \({@a1@}\times {@b1@}\times 10^{{@ind1@}+({@ind2@})} = {@ta1@}. \)</p>]]></text>
		</generalfeedback>
